data.description: A MUST SEE. One-story 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms lovely brick veneer home nestled in the beautiful neighborhood of Twin Oaks Village. Newly renovated. New roof was replaced in 2022. Fresh paint interior. New water resist laminate floor throughout, new water heater, new dish washer and new microwave. Ceramic tiles in wet areas. Updated kitchen including granite countertops with undermount sinks, new microwave, new dishwasher, and so much more. Kitchen stainless steel appliances. Breakfast bar. Open concept floor plan. Nice sized backyard great for family gatherings! Easy access and only few minutes to Westpark Toll Road, 99 Grand Parkway & Hwy 6. No flooded. Ready to move in. Schedule your appointment today!
